From: Uri Mashiach <uri.mashiach@compulab.co.il>
Date: Sun, 6 Sep 2020 17:22:21 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 32/55] iot-gate-imx8: enable CPU temperature read

Enable the user space temperature read from the CPU.

Signed-off-by: Uri Mashiach <uri.mashiach@compulab.co.il>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/iot-gate-imx8_defconfig | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/iot-gate-imx8_defconfig b/arch/arm64/configs/iot-gate-imx8_defconfig
index 8bcf3d91ce98..1dbe9585ec70 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/iot-gate-imx8_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/iot-gate-imx8_defconfig
@@ -381,6 +381,12 @@ CONFIG_SENSORS_LM90=m
 CONFIG_SENSORS_PWM_FAN=m
 CONFIG_SENSORS_INA2XX=m
 CONFIG_SENSORS_INA3221=m
+CONFIG_CPU_THERMAL=y
+CONFIG_THERMAL_EMULATION=y
+CONFIG_IMX_SC_THERMAL=y
+CONFIG_DEVICE_THERMAL=y
+CONFIG_IMX8MM_THERMAL=y
+CONFIG_QORIQ_THERMAL=y
 CONFIG_WATCHDOG=y
 CONFIG_ARM_SP805_WATCHDOG=y
 CONFIG_ARM_SBSA_WATCHDOG=y
